{"analytics_identifier":"PB1458","base_path":"/government/organisations/ethics-and-integrity-commission","content_id":"dce66d9b-2ed5-4249-8e38-885109128505","description":"The Ethics and Integrity Commission (EIC) was launched on 13 October 2025, replacing the Committee on Standards in Public Life (CSPL). The EIC promotes the highest standards in public life, reports to the Prime Minister on matters concerning ethical standards, and advises public authorities on the development of clear codes of conduct with effective oversight arrangements. The Commission is not a regulator and has no remit to investigate individual cases. The Ethics and Integrity Commission has a separate website. EIC is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Cabinet Office .","details":{"acronym":"EIC","alternative_format_contact_email":"contact@eic.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Ethics and Integrity Commission (EIC) was launched on 13 October 2025, replacing the Committee on Standards in Public Life (CSPL). The EIC promotes the highest standards in public life, reports to the Prime Minister on matters concerning ethical standards, and advises public authorities on the development of clear codes of conduct with effective oversight arrangements. The Commission is not a regulator and has no remit to investigate individual cases.</p>\n\n<p>The Ethics and Integrity Commission has a separate website.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Ethics and Integrity Commission\">EIC</abbr> is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/cabinet-office\">Cabinet Office</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"cabinet-office","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"Ethics and<br/>Integrity<br/>Commission","image":{"alt_text":"Ethics and Integrity Commission","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68eccc4ca8398380cb4acf5e/Ethics_and_Integrity_Commission_logo.png"}},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"exempt","updated_at":null,"url":"https://eic.independent-commission.uk/"},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"advisory_ndpb","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2025-10-13T10:54:20+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"PB1458","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/ethics-and-integrity-commission","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/ethics-and-integrity-commission","base_path":"/government/organisations/ethics-and-integrity-commission","content_id":"dce66d9b-2ed5-4249-8e38-885109128505","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-10-13T10:01:03Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Ethics and Integrity Commission","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ethics-and-integrity-commission","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_board_members":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/doug-chalmers","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/doug-chalmers","base_path":"/government/people/doug-chalmers","content_id":"b29ef073-deed-4334-8062-83539d83f81c","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Doug Chalmers CB DSO OBE","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/665879d40c8f88e868d333da/s465_cspl_colour_hr-5303_-_Doug__1___1_.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"3ef508bb-df8a-4f36-94f4-08e787191f81","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":2,"started_on":"2023-12-12T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"84754ecb-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Chair is responsible for leading the committee in:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>advising the Prime Minister about standards of conduct of all holders of public office</li>\n  <li>making recommendations for change to ensure the highest standards in public life</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The Chair also:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>leads and manages the work programme</li>\n  <li>acts as a spokesperson for the committee</li>\n  <li>consults with the relevant parliamentary committees and regulators</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-10-13T10:56:07Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chair, Committee on Standards in Public Life","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-12-12T16:24:57Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Doug Chalmers CB DSO OBE - Chair, Committee on Standards in Public Life","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"db0ed856-3020-4b65-88bb-6ebad28ad7cc","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2021-03-31T00:00:00+01:00","person_appointment_order":4990,"started_on":"2018-06-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"9a728e34-f54f-4512-b67f-ffc0e7dea43e","details":{"body":"<p>This role has been created by changes under the Defence Reform programme. Responsibilities will be updated in due course.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-04-01T16:12:26Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Deputy Chief of Defence Staff (Military Strategy and Operations)","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-08-04T09:37:47Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Lieutenant General Doug Chalmers - Deputy Chief of Defence Staff (Military Strategy and Operations)","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-10-24T08:13:32Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Doug Chalmers CB DSO OBE","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/doug-chalmers","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/governm